  <locale>en_US</locale>
  <definition><![CDATA[when a managers near suspicious vehicle occurs

definitions 
	set 'richable buildings' to the buildings of this managers near suspicious vehicle 
	where the range of this managers near suspicious vehicle contains each building ;
	
if the number of elements in 'richable buildings' is more than 0 then

for each building in 'richable buildings' :
	- emit a new alert where
		the vehicle is the vehicle of this managers near suspicious vehicle ,
		the rule is the name of this rule,
		the building is this building,
		;]]></definition>
</com.ibm.ia.designer.berl:BerlRule>
